I"8<p>I’ve compiled 10 years of my reading data and made good faith guesses at understanding the authors’ preferred gender, race/enthnicity, and geographic country of origin. (Not to classify or categorize their authors, but to gain insight into my own reading habits.) Here’s what I found…</p>

